Reported Manchester United target Francisco Trincao has spoken out on his future - and the Braga youngster, who has a reported &euro;30m release clause, is tight-lipped over rumours linking him with the club.<br />
<br />
&ldquo;I am doing my job,&quot; Trincao told Mais Futebol. &ldquo;Whether people are appreciating it or not, is not for me to comment. At this moment I am at Sporting Braga and I will do my best for the club.&rdquo;
